data.description: See agent only remarks: This delightful home boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Inside, a spacious layout reveals a modern kitchen with sleek backsplash-under cabinet lighting- and new stainless steel appliances. Custom enlarged walk-in shower in primary bath as well as new subway tile. Elegant shutters adorn windows, while customized bathroom mirrors and new fans enhance comfort. The living area features an upgraded fireplace mantle, bar corbels, and new pendant lighting, creating a cozy atmosphere. Fresh paint, new flooring, and an epoxy garage floor brighten every room. Outside, an extended deck with added lighting and updated fixtures elevate curb appeal. A brand new deck offers a perfect spot for morning coffee or entertaining. With its convenient location and move-in ready status, this home awaits its new owner! Convenient to dinning, shopping and walking trail. Fiber Optics internet.  Notice the attached update sheet as there are too many to list!
